{"tid":410562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地肉感網紅被好友出賣　零P圖竟獲網民大讚：五官是可以的","createTime":"2017-09-23T04:54:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-12T06:31:01.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3871256155565ea71b0c81ca22bc99979fb7c77e","tid":410562,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T04:54:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/120335/thumbnail/5c96afbd1e7325fe8fe22cdfb268e283.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F120335%2Fthumbnail%2F5c96afbd1e7325fe8fe22cdfb268e283.jpg&h=9ad84c43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n騙徒手法層出不窮，尤其在網絡世界，更加要「戴眼識人」！繼日前有內地網民在酒店泳池偶遇網紅女神自拍，踢爆對方鏡頭前後差別很大後，近日又有P圖高手出招對付另一網紅「小澤瑪麗甜甜」。她平日最愛上載牙籤腳、V煞臉、大眼高鼻的照片呃Like，誰知被網民「網紅扒皮」公開其日常照，並笑指她才是「照騙」界的神級高手。「小澤瑪麗甜甜」被公開零P圖（未經修改的照片）後，在微博大方回應指被好友出賣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/850220/xlarge/d70102a881d098bcb55d6c4fd9fc50a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F850220%2Fxlarge%2Fd70102a881d098bcb55d6c4fd9fc50a1.jpg&h=a1893bbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內地網紅「小澤瑪麗甜甜」在相中擁V煞臉、大眼、高鼻，而且上圍豐滿，絕對稱得上美女一名。（微博「網友扒皮」圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/850226/xlarge/a1962d493746b73c908d84c7c234e8cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F850226%2Fxlarge%2Fa1962d493746b73c908d84c7c234e8cd.jpg&h=d257bb2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/850225/xlarge/a6cf937bb576f790b79168432c476909.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F850225%2Fxlarge%2Fa6cf937bb576f790b79168432c476909.jpg&h=d1e09eda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/851159/xlarge/2b1da06dbe8ed29e815a3f6eb1e4d98a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F851159%2Fxlarge%2F2b1da06dbe8ed29e815a3f6eb1e4d98a.jpg&h=16567bed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n該網民日前一口氣上載3張「小澤瑪麗甜甜」的「日常照」及3張沒有P圖的真面目照，相中這位名為「小澤瑪麗甜甜」的網紅，在微博自稱是「上海英模文化發展有限公司簽約模特」，並有3萬多個粉絲。在她的「日常照」中，可見她身材纖瘦、擁驕人上圍、V煞臉等，單憑照片而言，絕對是靚女一名。<br />\n<br />\n但現實總是殘酷的，該網民公開的正面照中，發現「小澤瑪麗甜甜」原來是肉感靚女，隨即引來網民熱議，並在她的微博洗版指：「我懷疑人生了」、「這同一個人嗎？」、「終於知道為什麼的瘦，胸還那麼大的人什麼原因啦，全是P的。」不過亦有不少網民力撐「小澤瑪麗甜甜」：「五官是可以的」、「只有我感覺沒P也挺好看嗎？」、「至少胸是真的」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/850246/xlarge/f5b649cc691edf9fa51a154b676f23f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F850246%2Fxlarge%2Ff5b649cc691edf9fa51a154b676f23f2.jpg&h=828a1a7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網民在微博上載「小澤瑪麗甜甜」的真面目，引來大批網民熱議。（微博「網友扒皮」圖片）<br />\n<br />\n其後「小澤瑪麗甜甜」在微博大方回應指被好友出賣，原圖是她的朋友放上網：「居然這麼害我，我真的想不到，她剛剛回我說，免費讓你紅一把不開心嗎？」她又坦承：「其實我的妝前妝後差距特大，之後要是有時間我可以直播，或者錄視頻給大家分享化妝和修圖的，還有希望大家給我一點時間，我一定會瘦回去的。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/850248/xlarge/934f16460ea92cccf7e76709052c888c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F850248%2Fxlarge%2F934f16460ea92cccf7e76709052c888c.jpg&h=9c9267ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/850249/xlarge/58601ec1248f1631a1f730a3759b5b7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F850249%2Fxlarge%2F58601ec1248f1631a1f730a3759b5b7e.jpg&h=f61a7eaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/850298/xlarge/9c8421ec646645a8e14d318db8105c71.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F850298%2Fxlarge%2F9c8421ec646645a8e14d318db8105c71.jpg&h=64e07131&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/850300/xlarge/2e0a1db802d2e26d9a64c550b1094cc3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F850300%2Fxlarge%2F2e0a1db802d2e26d9a64c550b1094cc3.jpg&h=1357afa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實「網絡詐騙」又豈止一單，早前有另一位內地網紅度假時，被網民撞破在泳池邊不斷自拍，誰知該網紅真面目同樣是「肉」女一名，嚇到網民立即將鏡頭內外對比照上傳網絡，引起熱議。<br />\n<br />\n（微博、東森新聞）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/851015/xlarge/1fdea2ca121955f4c45de7f1f2c0068f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F851015%2Fxlarge%2F1fdea2ca121955f4c45de7f1f2c0068f.jpg&h=7a0cbaee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/851014/xlarge/dc6717f7a80e8c5ff77f6f9189895457.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F851014%2Fxlarge%2Fdc6717f7a80e8c5ff77f6f9189895457.jpg&h=6bb1cb43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/851013/xlarge/0666e164c2a95144f58ab864007b492c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F851013%2Fxlarge%2F0666e164c2a95144f58ab864007b492c.jpg&h=1cc4ae6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/851012/xlarge/1e1f5c226b0ecc7d5c22e4976e3c1c7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F851012%2Fxlarge%2F1e1f5c226b0ecc7d5c22e4976e3c1c7d.jpg&h=28a0eba1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n撰文：李思朗<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1/120335/%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E8%82%89%E6%84%9F%E7%B6%B2%E7%B4%85%E8%A2%AB%E5%A5%BD%E5%8F%8B%E5%87%BA%E8%B3%A3-%E9%9B%B6P%E5%9C%96%E7%AB%9F%E7%8D%B2%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E5%A4%A7%E8%AE%9A-%E4%BA%94%E5%AE%98%E6%98%AF%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E7%9A%84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25A9%25B1%2F120335%2F%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E8%2582%2589%25E6%2584%259F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E7%25B4%2585%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E5%258F%258B%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25B3%25A3-%25E9%259B%25B6P%25E5%259C%2596%25E7%25AB%259F%25E7%258D%25B2%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25AE%259A-%25E4%25BA%2594%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%258F%25AF%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E7%259A%2584&d=QHPTG5eaz2GpMCGqPCcVezA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=593ef398\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1/120335/%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E8%82%89%E6%84%9F%E7%B6%B2%E7%B4%85%E8%A2%AB%E5%A5%BD%E5%8F%8B%E5%87%BA%E8%B3%A3-%E9%9B%B6P%E5%9C%96%E7%AB%9F%E7%8D%B2%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E5%A4%A7%E8%AE%9A-%E4%BA%94%E5%AE%98%E6%98%AF%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E7%9A%84</a>"},{"pid":"18eb42356a77ada069aa3e78f103512d7adec8a4","tid":410562,"uid":149041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T05:01:51.000Z","msg":"睇相都唔靚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e43d74262acf53097b78cda97f9f7f0797349c4b","tid":410562,"uid":36035,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T05:11:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b03677c07d03c787f29dc405e33c6ee87847ad09","tid":410562,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T05:13:32.000Z","msg":"死肥閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b559b307f78e3212e46499957203a5906aae0b39","tid":410562,"uid":60959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T06:27:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港代表Rose Ma，真人成隻豬咁，<span style=\"color: red;\">不過有得屌還是會屌的</span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1d3d24b3b77b26452c8bf806562017ad7a09a7f","tid":410562,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T06:31:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港代表Rose Ma，真人成隻豬咁，<span style=\"color: red;\">不過有得屌還是會屌的</span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji